author: jerenkrantz
msg: Allow user to specify --with-diffutils to indicate where their diff/diff3
should be detected.  Rework diff shell script detection as m4 macro.
* configure.in: Include ac-helpers/gnu-diff.m4.  Replace custom diffutils
code with the SVN_LIB_DIFFUTILS() m4 macro in ac-helpers/gnu-diff.m4
* ac-helpers/gnu-diff3.sh, ac-helpers/check-diff.sh: Removed
* ac-helpers/gnu-diff.m4: Added.

author: rooneg
msg: * subversion/include/svn_types.h
add doxygen markup to comments.

author: rooneg
msg: * subversion/include/svn_string.h
add doxygen markup to comments.  the format here is a little different than
that in the rest of the headers, with a large block of comments up right
under the copyright header, because it makes the comment show up on the
main doxygen html page for svn_string.h.  all the other ways of marking it
up that i was able to come up with ended up leaving this information on some
other out of the way page, which seemed like a bad thing for fundamental
information about these structures.  if this format bothers anyone, someone
with more doxygen-fu than me can find another way to do it.

author: rooneg
msg: * subversion/include/svn_delta.h
add doxygen markup to the comments.
* subversion/include/svn_auth.h
remove some remnants of our pre-doxygen commenting style that i accidently
missed the first time through this file.
